'''''Napomuceno's Will'''''  ni filime yerekana ikinamico ya Cape Verdean yasohotse 2017 iyobowe na [[Francisco Manso]], ishingiye ku gitabo cyitwa ''The Last Will and Testament of Senhor da Silva Araújo'' cyanditswe na Germano Almeida . <ref>https://mubi.com/films/napumocenos-will</ref> <ref>https://www.worldcat.org/title/testamento-do-sr-napumoceno-napumocenos-will/oclc/41177479</ref> 

== Icegeranyo ==
[[Dosiye:Ilhas_do_Barlavento.png|thumb| Ikarita y'Ibirwa bya Barlavento ya Cape Verde; Nyiricyubahiro Napumuceno ava muri São Nicolau (hagati) yerekeza i São Vicente (mu burengerazuba).]]
Napumoceno da Silva Araújo, umucuruzi ukize wa [[Kapu Veri|Cape Verde]], yarapfuye kandi atunguranye ategura mwishywa we, asiga umutungo we ku mukobwa utemewe. Amusigira kandi icyegeranyo cya kaseti aho amubwira amateka y'ubuzima bwe, uko yavuye mubukene agera ku ntsinzi no mu rwego, ndetse n'abagore benshi yakundaga mu nzira.  <ref>https://bfca.sitehost.iu.edu/collections/films/films_O.shtml</ref>

