== Kurekura ==
''Napomuceno's Will bwerekanwe bwa'' mbere muri Festival de Gramado, Burezili muri Kanama 1997<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/napomuceno-s-will/m0crvvx9?hl=en</ref>. 

Yakiriye ibitekerezo byiza, ''Variety'' ishima Chico Díaz byumwihariko. <ref>https://variety.com/1998/film/reviews/testamento-1200454367/</ref> Kuri ''Chronicle ya San Francisco'', Mick LaSalle yanditse ko "[Araujo ya Xavier] ari clown, ariko imwe ifite imbaraga kandi ifite igitekerezo kimwe kuburyo byumvikana impamvu akurura abagore kandi agatsinda mubucuruzi<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/1999/04/30/movies/film-review-what-do-you-call-a-man-who-s-suddenly-rich-dad.html</ref>. Hamwe nubwitonzi bwibutsa Roberto Benigni, akoresha ijwi rye nkigikoresho gisetsa gitangaje, akazamuka akagera kumatwi mugihe cyo kwiyemera no gukabya<ref>https://www.carnavalrecoleta.cl/host-https-pro.imdb.com/title/tt1524291/?ref_=tt_pub_cst_kf_919</ref>. Muri icyo gihe, Xavier aduha ibihe byo kwambika ubusa umutima, igihe Araujo yiyitiriye, kandi tubona mu bubabare bwe. " 

Muri ''Filime Nyafurika Yitwa Lusophone'', Paulo de Medeiros yinubiye ko iyi filime yirengagije ibivugwa mu bukoloni mu gitabo cy’umwimerere, yerekana ko hamwe n’umuyobozi w’Abanyaportigale hamwe n’abayireba, iyi filime ikubiyemo ibitekerezo bya "Lusotropicaliste" cyangwa igamije kwibagirwa ubukoloni<ref>http://www.librarything.com/work/3461914</ref>. 

